title: Dinner Club
overview: The Swiss 3-Michelin-star chef Andreas Caminada embarks on a culinary journey to six different countries with six German-speaking celebrities, including actress Karoline Herfurth. In each episode, Caminada and one of the participants go in search of classic dishes, unusual ingredients and unique culinary experiences. At the end, the respective duo prepares a dinner for all the guests of the dinner club, bringing home the flavors and drinks tasted on the trip, along with the associated adventures and extraordinary stories behind each dish.
